eshop@mcmichael.on.ca or by phone (1 888 213 1121 or 416 893 1121) to
obtain an original copy of your invoice.

All items must be returned in original condition with the McMichael E-Shop
invoice.

When returning the item(s) to our Customer Service, please indicate on the
back of the invoice, or in an attached letter, the reasons for the return.

